title: FC Nordjylland
text: FC Nordjylland was the professional team of <a href="Denmark">Danish</a> <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club <a href="Aalborg%20Chang">Aalborg Chang</a> from <a href="2001-02%20in%20Danish%20football">season 2001–02</a> until its liquidation at the end of <a href="2003-04%20in%20Danish%20football">season 2003–04</a>. The team earned promotion to <a href="Danish%201st%20Division">Danish 1st Division</a> in its final season of existence but had to be disbanded after the main sponsor withdrew his financial support.
